# ðŸ©º Anti-Diabetic Drug Usage Analysis  
### End-to-End Python Data Analysis Project

This project analyzes *anti-diabetic drug usage* using a dummy healthcare dataset.  
It demonstrates *data cleaning, exploration, visualization, and insights generation* â€” essential skills for a *Data Analyst*.

---

## ðŸ“Œ Project Objectives

- Clean and prepare patient prescription data  
- Understand drug usage patterns  
- Analyze patient demographics  
- Visualize trends using charts  
- Build a beginner-friendly analytics project for portfolio  

---## ðŸ§  Key Insights

- *Metformin* is the most prescribed anti-diabetic drug  
- Patients aged *50â€“60* have the highest prescription counts  
- Both genders show similar patterns, with slightly higher insulin usage in females  
- The cost of medication varies significantly depending on the drug type  

