## ðŸ“‘ Dataset Description

| Column | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Patient_ID | Unique ID for each patient || Age | Patient age |
| Gender | M or F |
| Drug_Name | Prescribed anti-diabetic drug |
| Diagnosis | Diabetes type |
| Prescription_Date | Date of prescription |
| Dose | Drug dosage |
| Cost | Cost of medication |

Dataset is artificially generated for learning purposes.

